'''Head Guards''' are elite versions of the [[Guard (Shayzien)|Shayzien guards]] and are found around the kingdom of [[Kourend]]. They wield a [[dragon longsword]] along with a [[dragon sq shield]], and wear [[Shayzien armour]].

